WEBVTT

00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:11.560
Who's shooting?Sorry. It

00:00:13.520 --> 00:00:14.400
had to be done. There's

00:00:16.720 --> 00:00:17.320
no running now.

00:00:22.640 --> 00:00:25.560
The ranger's coming about! The Spaniards

00:00:25.680 --> 00:00:28.640
have got man in the rigging! Fire,

00:00:28.640 --> 00:00:30.720
Mr. Dufrayne. Everything you've got.

00:00:31.200 --> 00:00:32.320
Don't waste this moment.

00:00:51.040 --> 00:00:51.800
Open fire!

00:01:12.080 --> 00:01:13.040
You ready with this turn

00:01:16.640 --> 00:01:18.960
up?The rage is opening fire!

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:30.440
Catch it! Fire!

00:01:37.800 --> 00:01:38.720
She's coming about!

00:01:42.080 --> 00:01:42.280
Fire!

00:01:52.400 --> 00:01:52.880
Fire!

